OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with some light rain in the
OL,7,Fwest, staying dry in the east. The
OL,8,Frest of the night will be cloudy with
OL,9,Fsome occasional rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FSome bright spells in the
OL,12,Fnorth and east at first. Otherwise
OL,13,Fcloudy with spells of rain moving east
OL,14,Fduring the day, but drier in the north.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,17,Fchangeable, often cloudy and windy few
OL,18,Fdays with spells of rain, occasionally
OL,19,Fheavy and persistent in the west. Best
OL,20,Fof the drier, brighter spells around
OL,21,Fthe Moray Firth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
